TY  - JOUR
TI  - Stabilization of the Canadian Dollar: 1952-1960
AU  - Pippinger, John E.
AU  - Phillips, Llad
AB  - [In this paper we construct a model that describes the behavior of the foreign exchange market and Exchange Fund. Cross-spectral and regression analysis of daily data are used to show that official intervention contributed significantly to the short-run stability of Canadian exchange rates.]
