TY  - JOUR
TI  - On the Uniqueness of Competitive Equilibrium: Part I, Unbounded Demand
AU  - Pearce, I. F.
AU  - Wise, J.
AB  - [This paper is concerned with general equilibrium under a weakened version of Walras' Law. Conditions for uniqueness of equilibrium are derived which include the more standard conditions as a special case and which are at the same time free of some of the weaknesses of received theory.]
