TY  - JOUR
TI  - Conditions for the Existence of Cycles under Majority and Non-Minority Rules
AU  - Fine, Kit
AB  - [This paper simplifies and extends some previous work on domain restriction. With the help of an easy arithmetical result, two types of necessary and sufficient conditions are established for transitivity and quasi-transitivity under majority rule and transitivity under non-minority rule.]
